U.K Court Rules Dewani Can Be Extradited to South Africa on Murder Charges

-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   S c i n t a
-- 
2011-08-10T11:43:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-10/court-rules-dewani-can-be-extradited-to-south-africa-on-murder-charges.html
A U.K. judge ruled that Shrien
Dewani, who is accused of killing his wife on their honeymoon,
can be extradited to  South Africa  to face charges. The judge
sent the case case to the Secretary of State for a further
ruling on whether Dewani should be extradited, according to an
e-mailed statement from the court today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Scinta at 
 cscinta@bloomberg.net  